Thanks for the upload, I couldn't find my disc anywhere.

All you have to do is:
1. Unrar one of the rar files. 
2. Use Virtual CloneDrive to mount the unrar file. 
3. Go to the 'Computer' and click the drive of the unrar file. 
4. Install it and you're done! Have fun.
